title: Armored Core 4 NTSC XBOX360-APATHY
description:
Armored Core 4 is set in the near future in an alternate universe where a great war has left the nations of Earth devastated and corporations have taken over the role of the government. The game features a system for personalized customization of the player's mech and an online mode where players can battle each other over Xbox Live. 

Region Free....: No
